entries.title_d: Show your loyalty to Jabba by destroying the fighter pilots Lady Valaria hired to replace you
entries.title: Yavin System: Hunt down Valarian replacements
entries.split_quest_alert: You must hunt down two (2) more targets in this zone!
entries.quest_target_d: An old spice runner that worked some time for Jabba
entries.quest_escort_d: Required to destroy the escort to complete the mission
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Valarian's new hired killer managed to elude you.  Perhaps she was right in letting you get away. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Leave no one left alive, pilot! Destroy the target's escort, now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: Success! Valarian's hired killer is now history...
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Right on time.  Their tracking information should have been uploaded to you. Have at them. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 It should please you to know that she hired three pilots to replace you.  We have the first one coming in shortly. \#pcontrast3 >
